Google is empowering data scientists and researchers with the deployment of the Data Science Agent to its Colab platform. For those unfamiliar, Google Colab is a free, cloud-hosted Jupyter Notebook environment allowing users to write and execute Python code within their browser. By providing free access to Google Cloud GPUs and TPUs, Colab has become... Read more »

title: Google deploys Data Science Agent to Colab users
